&lt;p&gt;The Director will work in close partnership with the broader U.S. Market Access and collaborate closely with cross-functional partners including brand marketing, sales, HEOR, medical affairs, patient services, and operations to ensure strategic alignment and execution excellence&lt;/p&gt;
