ders, including the C-Suite. This position reports to the Senior Director, Regional Marketing Lead and will work in very close partnership with Sales, the TGCT and Desmoid Tumor Brand Teams and the broader U.S. Rare Tumor Marketing Team.&lt;/p&gt;
